  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your massive ears are your pride and joy, and other goblins claim you can hear a flea scream as it falls off a goblin dog.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Goblin</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>While this might not quite be the case, you gain a +2 bonus on all Perception checks made to hear noises. Additionally, you can hear noises that normally only dogs or other animals can hear, like the sound of a dog whistle.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Pathfinder Society</strong></p>\n<p>Only legal goblin PCs are allowed to take this trait.</p>",
